quran[10{c,v,t}:
25,68,aur woh jo khuda ke sath kisi aur mabood ko nahi pkarte aur jin jandaar ko maar daalna khuda ne haraamkiya hai is ko qatal nahi karte magar jaaiz tareeq par ( yani Shariat ke mutabiq ) aur badkaari nahi karte. aur jo yeh kaam kere ga sakht gunah mein mubtala hoga
25,69,qayamat ke din is ko dona azaab hoga aur zillat o khawari se hamesha is mein rahay ga
25,70,magar jis ne tauba ki aur imaan laya aur achay kaam kiye to aisay logon ke gunaaho ko khuda nakiyon se badal day ga. aur khuda to bakhsnay wala meharban hai
25,71,aur jo tauba karta aur amal naik karta hai to be shak woh khuda ki taraf rujoo karta hai
25,72,aur woh jo jhooti gawahi nahi dete aur jab un ko behooda cheezon ke paas se guzarnay ka ittafaq ho to buzurgana andaaz se guzarte hain
25,73,aur woh ke jab un ko perwar-digaar ki baatein samjhai jati hain to unn par andhay aur behray ho kar nahi girtay ( balkay ghhor se suntay hain )
25,74,aur woh jo ( khuda se ) dua mangte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko hamari biwion ki taraf se ( dil ka chain ) aur aulaad ki taraf se aankhh ki thandak ataa farma aur hamein parhaiz garon ka imam bana
25,75,un ( sifaat ke ) logon ko un ke sabr ke badlay ounchay ounchay mehal diye jayen ge. aur wahan farishtay un se dua o slaam ke sath mulaqaat karen ge
25,76,is mein woh hamesha rahen ge. aur woh tehrnay aur rehne ki bohat hi umdah jagah hai
25,77,keh do ke agar tum ( khuda ko ) nahi pkarte to mera perwar-digaar bhi tumhari kuch parwa nahi karta. tum ne takzieeb ki hai so is ki saza ( tumahray liye ) lazim hogi
